Jorgo Chatzimarkakis, a member of 
European Parliament representing  Germany 's Free Democratic 
Party, discusses Greece's economy, fiscal targets and 
relationship with Germany.  He talks from Athens with Linzie Janis on Bloomberg 
Television's "Countdown." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 04:56
 